Jake Richardson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jake_Richardson 0 Jacob Matthew Richardson (born February 20, 1985) is an American actor, currently acting mostly in TV series. He is perhaps best known for his roles in the film Honey, We Shrunk Ourselves and the TV series Fudge.
